      "acceptanceCriteria": "Experimental test conditions match intended COU operating points within specified tolerances; fluid properties and boundary conditions documented.",
      "rationale": "Experimental flow rates and rotational speeds match nominal COU conditions. Blood analog viscosity deviates from physiological range at two test points. Boundary condition documentation complete."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
