      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic pump geometry, which is the COU device. However, experiments used saline-based blood analog rather than whole blood, and hematocrit was not matched to clinical range. Operating envelope coverage partial — only 3 of 5 COU points tested experimentally."
    },
