      "rationale": "k-omega SST turbulence model selected without comparison to alternative models. Power-Law hemolysis model not benchmarked against Giersiepen or modified Bludszuweit models. Model form uncertainty unquantified — major epistemic gap at MRL 5."
    },
    {
