      "rationale": "Monte Carlo UQ performed for geometric tolerances and inlet boundary conditions. Blood viscosity and hemolysis model coefficients treated as deterministic; their uncertainty not propagated. Partial credit — key input uncertainties excluded from UQ sweep."
