    "rationale": "Despite multiple credibility factor gaps and achieved levels below required levels across all 13 factors, the assessment is accepted for submission to the regulatory dossier as a documented record of current model credibility status. The decision reflects acceptance of the evidence package as complete documentation, not acceptance of the model for clinical use. All gaps are flagged for remediation prior to device submission.",
